00:35:33,680 --> 00:35:35,300
ELIZA:
Helpless...

692
00:35:35,300 --> 00:35:37,620
ANGELICA:
And I know she is...

693
00:35:37,620 --> 00:35:39,060
ELIZA:
Helpless...

694
00:35:39,060 --> 00:35:41,400
ANGELICA:
And her eyes are just...

695
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:43,160
ELIZA:
Helpless...

696
00:35:43,160 --> 00:35:44,980
ANGELICA:
And I realize

697
00:35:44,980 --> 00:35:49,560
Three fundamental truths
