698
00:35:49,560 --> 00:35:51,120
HAMILTON
Where are you taking me?

699
00:35:51,120 --> 00:35:52,520
ANGELICA
I'm about to change your life.

700
00:35:52,520 --> 00:35:55,000
HAMILTON
Then by all means, lead the way.

701
00:35:55,000 --> 00:35:59,140
