705
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:13,840
ELIZA:
Elizabeth Schuyler. It's a pleasure to meet you.

706
00:36:13,840 --> 00:36:16,360
HAMILTON: Schuyler?
ANGELICA: My sister!

707
00:36:16,360 --> 00:36:16,380
