00:38:00,500 --> 00:38:03,500
And I know

733
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:13,940
He will never be satisfied
I will never be satisfied

734
00:38:22,340 --> 00:38:25,780
LAURENS:
I may not live to see our glory!

