00:38:25,780 --> 00:38:28,780
MULLIGAN/LAFAYETTE:
I may not live to see our glory!

736
00:38:28,780 --> 00:38:31,780
LAURENS
But I've seen wonders great and small.

737
00:38:31,780 --> 00:38:34,780
MULLIGAN/LAFAYETTE:
I've seen wonders great and small.

738
00:38:34,780 --> 00:38:37,780
LAURENS:
Cuz if the tomcat can get married,

739
00:38:37,780 --> 00:38:40,780
MULLIGAN/LAFAYETTE:
If Alexander can get married-

