00:38:40,780 --> 00:38:43,040
LAURENS:
There's hope for our ass, after all!

741
00:38:43,040 --> 00:38:45,240
LAFAYETTE:
Raise a glass to freedom.

742
00:38:45,240 --> 00:38:48,860
LAURENS/MULLIGAN:
Hey! Something you will never see again!

743
