No, these guys should go.

772
00:39:38,720 --> 00:39:39,320
LAFAYETTE: What?
LAURENS: No!

773
00:39:39,320 --> 00:39:40,180
HAMILTON:
Leave us alone.

774
00:39:40,180 --> 00:39:41,000
MULLIGAN:
Man...

775
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:42,580
HAMILTON:
It's alright, Burr.

776
00:39:42,580 --> 00:39:45,280
I wish you'd brought this girl
with you tonight, Burr.

777
00:39:45,280 --> 00:39:48,060
BURR:
You're very kind, but I'm afraid it's unlawful, sir.

778
00:39:48,060 --> 00:39:48,800
HAMILTON:
What do you mean?

779
00:39:48,800 --> 00:39:49,760
BURR:
She's married.

780
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:50,240
HAMILTON:
I see.

781
00:39:50,240 --> 00:39:52,420
BURR:
She's married to a British officer.

782
00:39:52,420 --> 00:39:53,280
HAMILTON:
Oh shit...

783
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:58,720
BURR:
Congrats again, Alexander. Smile more.

784
00:39:58,720 --> 00:40:02,180
I'll see you on the other side of the war.

785
00:40:02,180 --> 00:40:05,180
