And if there's a reason I'm by her side
when so many have tried

797
00:41:02,900 --> 00:41:08,100
then I'm willing to wait for it.
I'm willing to wait for it.

798
00:41:09,020 --> 00:41:13,060
My grandfather was a fire
of brimstone preacher,

799
00:41:14,040 --> 00:41:18,120
But there are things that the
homilies and hymns won't teach ya.

800
00:41:19,560 --> 00:41:21,680
My mother was a genius

801
00:41:21,680 --> 00:41:23,980
My father commanded respect.

802
00:41:23,980 --> 00:41:29,300
