Awesome. Wow.

1128
01:00:59,200 --> 01:01:03,060
Do you have a clue what happens now?

1129
01:01:03,060 --> 01:01:11,260
Oceans rise, empires fall
It's much harder when it's all your call

1130
01:01:11,260 --> 01:01:15,620
All alone, across the sea

1131
01:01:15,620 --> 01:01:24,600
