1133
01:01:56,600 --> 01:02:00,680
BURR:
Dear Theodosia what to say to you

1134
01:02:00,680 --> 01:02:04,860
You have my eyes
You have your mother's name

1135
01:02:04,860 --> 01:02:10,960
When you came into the world
you cried and it broke my heart

1136
