HAMILTON:
Oh, Phillip when you smile I am undone, my son

1145
01:03:16,500 --> 01:03:21,900
Look at my son
Pride is not the word I'm looking for

1146
01:03:22,940 --> 01:03:26,420
There is so much more inside me now

1147
01:03:27,360 --> 01:03:34,400
Oh, Phillip you outshine the
morning sun, my son

1148
01:03:34,400 --> 01:03:43,360
When you smile, I fall apart
and I thought I was so smart

1149
