1150
01:03:47,440 --> 01:03:49,120
BURR:
My father wasn't around

1151
01:03:49,120 --> 01:03:49,980
HAMILTON:
I swear that

1152
01:03:49,980 --> 01:03:53,440
HAMILTON/BURR:
I'll be around for you

1153
01:03:53,440 --> 01:03:56,440
HAMILTON:
I'll do whatever it takes

1154
01:03:56,440 --> 01:03:58,420
BURR:
I'll make a million mistakes

1155
01:03:58,420 --> 01:04:02,400
HAMILTON/BURR:
I'll make the world safe and sound for you

1156
01:04:04,420 --> 01:04:07,480
You'll come of age with our young nation

1157
01:04:08,180 --> 01:04:12,480
We'll bleed and fight for you
We'll make it right for you

1158
01:04:12,480 --> 01:04:16,460
If we lay a strong enough foundation

1159
01:04:16,460 --> 01:04:16,480
We'll pass it on to you
We'll give the world to you
