We'll pass it on to you
We'll give the world to you

1161
01:04:21,060 --> 01:04:27,420
And you'll blow us all away
Someday, someday

1162
01:04:30,180 --> 01:04:37,440
Yeah, you'll blow us all away
Someday, someday

1163
01:04:43,060 --> 01:04:45,860
LAURENS:
I may not live to see our glory.

1164
01:04:46,780 --> 01:04:48,600
ELIZA:
Alexander? There's a letter for you.

1165
01:04:48,600 --> 01:04:50,540
HAMILTON:
It's from John Laurens. I'll read it later.

1166
01:04:50,540 --> 01:04:53,540
LAURENS:
But I will gladly join the fight.

1167
