1191
01:06:23,660 --> 01:06:25,340
BURR:
Co-counsel. Hamilton, sit down,

1192
01:06:25,340 --> 01:06:28,240
Our client Levi Weeks is innocent.
Call your first witness

1193
01:06:28,240 --> 01:06:29,240
That's all you had to say!

1194
01:06:29,240 --> 01:06:30,880
HAMILTON:
Okay! One more thing--

1195
