I am not throwin' away my shot!
(Just you wait!)

1307
01:12:02,640 --> 01:12:05,060
I am Alexander Hamilton!
(Alexander Hamilton! Hamilton!)

1308
01:12:05,060 --> 01:12:09,840
(Just you wait!)
I am not throwin' away my shot!

1309
01:12:12,560 --> 01:12:14,940
ACT II

